      "prompt": "请创建一个完整的 HTML5 游戏。游戏描述：创建一个贪食蛇游戏。\n                    \n重要技术要求：\n1. 单个 HTML 文件\n2. 使用 Canvas API\n3. Canvas 尺寸必须为 360x640 像素（9:16 竖屏比例）\n4. 在 JavaScript 中设置：canvas.width = 360; canvas.height = 640;\n5. 在 CSS 中设置：canvas { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n6. 包含完整游戏循环\n7. 有得分系统\n8. 确保有趣可玩\n\n只返回 HTML 代码，不要其他说明。",
      "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>贪食蛇游戏</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        #gameContainer {\n            position: relative;\n            width: 360px;\n            height: 640px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        canvas {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            border-radius: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        #uiOverlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        \n        #scoreDisplay {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        #scoreValue {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            margin-left: 8px;\n        }\n        \n        #highScoreDisplay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 50px;\n            left: 15px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            font-size: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        #highScoreValue {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            margin-left: 4px;\n        }\n        \n        #instructions {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        \n        .menu-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.9);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            pointer-events: auto;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        .menu-title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.5);\n        }\n        \n        .menu-subtitle {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n        \n        .menu-score {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n        }\n        \n        .menu-instruction {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n        }\n        \n        .menu-button {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4fd1c5, #38b2ac);\n            border: none;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 25px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n            pointer-events: auto;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.3);\n        }\n        \n        .menu-button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.4);\n        }\n        \n        .hidden {\n            display: none !important;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"gameContainer\">\n        <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\"></canvas>\n        <div id=\"uiOverlay\">\n            <div id=\"scoreDisplay\">\n                得分: <span id=\"scoreValue\">0</span>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"highScoreDisplay\">\n                最高分: <span id=\"highScoreValue\">0</span>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"instructions\">\n                方向键或WASD控制移动 | P键暂停\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 菜单界面 -->\n        <div id=\"menuScreen\" class=\"menu-overlay\">\n            <div class=\"menu-title\">贪食蛇</div>\n            <div class=\"menu-subtitle\">经典游戏，挑战你的反应速度！</div>\n            <div class=\"menu-instruction\">使用方向键或WASD控制蛇的移动</div>\n            <div class=\"menu-instruction\">吃到食物可以增长身体并得分</div>\n            <div class=\"menu-instruction\">不要撞到墙壁或自己的身体</div>\n            <button class=\"menu-button\" id=\"startButton\">开始游戏</button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 暂停界面 -->\n        <div id=\"pauseScreen\" class=\"menu-overlay hidden\">\n            <div class=\"menu-title\">游戏暂停</div>\n            <div class=\"menu-subtitle\">休息一下，准备继续挑战</div>\n            <button class=\"menu-button\" id=\"resumeButton\">继续游戏</button>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 游戏结束界面 -->\n        <div id=\"gameOverScreen\" class=\"menu-overlay hidden\">\n            <div class=\"menu-title\">游戏结束</div>\n            <div class=\"menu-score\">最终得分: <span id=\"finalScore\">0</span></div>\n            <div class=\"menu-score\">最高分: <span id=\"finalHighScore\">0</span></div>\n            <button class=\"menu-button\" id=\"restartButton\">重新开始</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // 游戏常量\n        const CANVAS_WIDTH = 360;\n        const CANVAS_HEIGHT = 640;\n        const GRID_SIZE = 20;\n        const GRID_WIDTH = Math.floor(CANVAS_WIDTH / GRID_SIZE);\n        const GRID_HEIGHT = Math.floor(CANVAS_HEIGHT / GRID_SIZE);\n        const GAME_AREA_TOP = 60; // 留出顶部空间给得分显示\n        const GAME_AREA_HEIGHT = CANVAS_HEIGHT - GAME_AREA_TOP - 40; // 底部留出空间给说明\n        \n        // 游戏状态\n        let gameState = 'menu'; // menu, playing, paused, gameover\n        let score = 0;\n        let highScore = parseInt(localStorage.getItem('snakeHighScore')) || 0;\n        \n        // 蛇相关\n        let snake = [];\n        let direction = { x: 1, y: 0 };\n        let nextDirection = { x: 1, y: 0 };\n        let lastMoveTime = 0;\n        let moveInterval = 150; // 移动间隔（毫秒）\n        \n        // 食物相关\n        let food = { x: 0, y: 0 };\n        let specialFood = null;\n        let specialFoodTimer = 0;\n        \n        // 游戏循环相关\n        let lastTime = 0;\n        let deltaTime = 0;\n        \n        // 初始化Canvas\n        const canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\n        const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n        canvas.width = CANVAS_WIDTH;\n        canvas.height = CANVAS_HEIGHT;\n        \n        // UI元素\n        const scoreValue = document.getElementById('scoreValue');\n        const highScoreValue = document.getElementById('highScoreValue');\n        const menuScreen = document.getElementById('menuScreen');\n        const pauseScreen = document.getElementById('pauseScreen');\n        const gameOverScreen = document.getElementById('gameOverScreen');\n        const finalScore = document.getElementById('finalScore');\n        const finalHighScore = document.getElementById('finalHighScore');\n        \n        // 更新UI显示\n        function updateUI() {\n            scoreValue.textContent = score;\n            highScoreValue.textContent = highScore;\n            finalScore.textContent = score;\n            finalHighScore.textContent = highScore;\n        }\n        \n        // 重置游戏\n        function resetGame() {\n            // 初始化蛇（从中间开始）\n            snake = [\n                { x: Math.floor(GRID_WIDTH / 2), y: Math.floor(GRID_HEIGHT / 2) },\n                { x: Math.floor(GRID_WIDTH / 2) - 1, y: Math.floor(GRID_HEIGHT / 2) },\n                { x: Math.floor(GRID_WIDTH / 2) - 2, y: Math.floor(GRID_HEIGHT / 2) }\n            ];\n            \n            direction = { x: 1, y: 0 };\n            nextDirection = { x: 1, y: 0 };\n            score = 0;\n            moveInterval = 150;\n            \n            // 生成食物\n            generateFood();\n            specialFood = null;\n            specialFoodTimer = 0;\n            \n            updateUI();\n        }\n        \n        // 生成普通食物\n        function generateFood() {\n            let validPosition = false;\n            while (!validPosition) {\n                food.x = Math.floor(Math.random() * GRID_WIDTH);\n                food.y = Math.floor(Math.random() * (GAME_AREA_HEIGHT / GRID_SIZE)) + Math.floor(GAME_AREA_TOP / GRID_SIZE);\n                \n                // 确保食物不会生成在蛇身上\n                validPosition = true;\n                for (let segment of snake) {\n                    if (segment.x === food.x && segment.y === food.y) {\n                        validPosition = false;\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 生成特殊食物（金色，得分更高）\n        function generateSpecialFood() {\n            if (specialFood !== null) return;\n            \n            let validPosition = false;\n            while (!validPosition) {\n                specialFood = {\n                    x: Math.floor(Math.random() * GRID_WIDTH),\n                    y: Math.floor(Math.random() * (GAME_AREA_HEIGHT / GRID_SIZE)) + Math.floor(GAME_AREA_TOP / GRID_SIZE),\n                    timer: 5000 // 5秒后消失\n                };\n                \n                // 确保特殊食物不会生成在蛇身上或普通食物位置\n                validPosition = true;\n                for (let segment of snake) {\n                    if (segment.x === specialFood.x && segment.y === specialFood.y) {\n                        validPosition = false;\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n                \n                if (specialFood.x === food.x && specialFood.y === food.y) {\n                    validPosition = false;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏逻辑更新\n        function update(deltaTime) {\n            if (gameState !== 'playing') return;\n            \n            // 更新特殊食物计时器\n            if (specialFood) {\n                specialFood.timer -= deltaTime;\n                if (specialFood.timer <= 0) {\n                    specialFood = null;\n                }\n            }\n            \n            // 随机生成特殊食物（5%的概率）\n            if (specialFood === null && Math.random() < 0.005) {\n                generateSpecialFood();\n            }\n            \n            // 蛇的移动计时\n            lastMoveTime += deltaTime;\n            if (lastMoveTime >= moveInterval) {\n                lastMoveTime = 0;\n                \n                // 更新方向\n                direction = { ...nextDirection };\n                \n                // 计算新的头部位置\n                const head = snake[0];\n                const newHead = {\n                    x: head.x + direction.x,\n                    y: head.y + direction.y\n                };\n                \n                // 检查碰撞\n                if (checkCollision(newHead)) {\n                    gameOver();\n                    return;\n                }\n                \n                // 移动蛇\n                snake.unshift(newHead);\n                \n                // 检查是否吃到食物\n                let ateFood = false;\n                \n                // 检查普通食物\n                if (newHead.x === food.x && newHead.y === food.y) {\n                    score += 10;\n                    ateFood = true;\n                    generateFood();\n                    \n                    // 加快游戏速度\n                    if (moveInterval > 50) {\n                        moveInterval -= 2;\n                    }\n                }\n                \n                // 检查特殊食物\n                if (specialFood && newHead.x === specialFood.x && newHead.y === specialFood.y) {\n                    score += 50;\n                    ateFood = true;\n                    specialFood = null;\n                }\n                \n                // 如果没有吃到食物，移除尾部\n                if (!ateFood) {\n                    snake.pop();\n                }\n                \n                // 更新最高分\n                if (score > highScore) {\n                    highScore = score;\n                    localStorage.setItem('snakeHighScore', highScore);\n                }\n                \n                updateUI();\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 检查碰撞\n        function checkCollision(position) {\n            // 检查墙壁碰撞\n            if (position.x < 0 || position.x >= GRID_WIDTH || \n                position.y < Math.floor(GAME_AREA_TOP / GRID_SIZE) || \n                position.y >= Math.floor((GAME_AREA_TOP + GAME_AREA_HEIGHT) / GRID_SIZE)) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            \n            // 检查自身碰撞（跳过尾部，因为即将移动）\n            for (let i = 0; i < snake.length - 1; i++) {\n                if (position.x === snake[i].x && position.y === snake[i].y) {\n                    return true;\n                }\n            }\n            \n            return false;\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏结束\n        function gameOver() {\n            gameState = 'gameover';\n            gameOverScreen.classList.remove('hidden');\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏渲染\n        function render() {\n            // 清空画布\n            ctx.clearRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制背景\n            const gradient = ctx.createLinearGradient(0, 0, 0, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            gradient.addColorStop(0, '#1a1a2e');\n            gradient.addColorStop(1, '#16213e');\n            ctx.fillStyle = gradient;\n            ctx.fillRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制游戏区域背景\n            ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(22, 33, 62, 0.8)';\n            ctx.fillRect(0, GAME_AREA_TOP, CANVAS_WIDTH, GAME_AREA_HEIGHT);\n            \n            // 绘制网格线\n            ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.1)';\n            ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n            \n            // 垂直线\n            for (let x = 0; x <= GRID_WIDTH; x++) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(x * GRID_SIZE, GAME_AREA_TOP);\n                ctx.lineTo(x * GRID_SIZE, GAME_AREA_TOP + GAME_AREA_HEIGHT);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            \n            // 水平线\n            for (let y = 0; y <= Math.floor(GAME_AREA_HEIGHT / GRID_SIZE); y++) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(0, GAME_AREA_TOP + y * GRID_SIZE);\n                ctx.lineTo(CANVAS_WIDTH, GAME_AREA_TOP + y * GRID_SIZE);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            \n            // 绘制食物\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#ff6b6b';\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(\n                food.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                food.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                GRID_SIZE / 2 - 2,\n                0,\n                Math.PI * 2\n            );\n            ctx.fill();\n            \n            // 绘制特殊食物\n            if (specialFood) {\n                ctx.fillStyle = '#ffd700';\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(\n                    specialFood.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                    specialFood.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                    GRID_SIZE / 2 - 2,\n                    0,\n                    Math.PI * 2\n                );\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 绘制特殊食物光环\n                ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.5)';\n                ctx.lineWidth = 2;\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(\n                    specialFood.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                    specialFood.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                    GRID_SIZE / 2 + 2,\n                    0,\n                    Math.PI * 2\n                );\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            \n            // 绘制蛇\n            for (let i = 0; i < snake.length; i++) {\n                const segment = snake[i];\n                \n                // 蛇头和身体使用不同颜色\n                if (i === 0) {\n                    // 蛇头\n                    ctx.fillStyle = '#4fd1c5';\n                } else {\n                    // 蛇身（渐变效果）\n                    const colorValue = Math.max(100, 200 - i * 5);\n                    ctx.fillStyle = `rgb(${colorValue}, ${Math.floor(colorValue * 0.8)}, ${Math.floor(colorValue * 0.6)})`;\n                }\n                \n                // 绘制圆角矩形\n                const x = segment.x * GRID_SIZE + 1;\n                const y = segment.y * GRID_SIZE + 1;\n                const width = GRID_SIZE - 2;\n                const height = GRID_SIZE - 2;\n                const radius = 4;\n                \n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(x + radius, y);\n                ctx.lineTo(x + width - radius, y);\n                ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x + width, y, x + width, y + radius);\n                ctx.lineTo(x + width, y + height - radius);\n                ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x + width, y + height, x + width - radius, y + height);\n                ctx.lineTo(x + radius, y + height);\n                ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x, y + height, x, y + height - radius);\n                ctx.lineTo(x, y + radius);\n                ctx.quadraticCurveTo(x, y, x + radius, y);\n                ctx.closePath();\n                ctx.fill();\n                \n                // 蛇头绘制眼睛\n                if (i === 0) {\n                    ctx.fillStyle = 'white';\n                    \n                    // 根据方向调整眼睛位置\n                    let eyeOffsetX = 0;\n                    let eyeOffsetY = 0;\n                    \n                    if (direction.x === 1) { // 向右\n                        eyeOffsetX = 5;\n                        eyeOffsetY = -3;\n                    } else if (direction.x === -1) { // 向左\n                        eyeOffsetX = -5;\n                        eyeOffsetY = -3;\n                    } else if (direction.y === 1) { // 向下\n                        eyeOffsetX = 0;\n                        eyeOffsetY = 5;\n                    } else if (direction.y === -1) { // 向上\n                        eyeOffsetX = 0;\n                        eyeOffsetY = -5;\n                    }\n                    \n                    // 左眼\n                    ctx.beginPath();\n                    ctx.arc(\n                        segment.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2 + eyeOffsetX - 3,\n                        segment.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2 + eyeOffsetY,\n                        2,\n                        0,\n                        Math.PI * 2\n                    );\n                    ctx.fill();\n                    \n                    // 右眼\n                    ctx.beginPath();\n                    ctx.arc(\n                        segment.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2 + eyeOffsetX + 3,\n                        segment.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2 + eyeOffsetY,\n                        2,\n                        0,\n                        Math.PI * 2\n                    );\n                    ctx.fill();\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 输入处理\n        function handleInput(key, pressed) {\n            if (!pressed) return;\n            \n            switch (key) {\n                case 'ArrowUp':\n                case 'KeyW':\n                    if (direction.y !== 1) {\n                        nextDirection = { x: 0, y: -1 };\n                    }\n                    break;\n                case 'ArrowDown':\n                case 'KeyS':\n                    if (direction.y !== -1) {\n                        nextDirection = { x: 0, y: 1 };\n                    }\n                    break;\n                case 'ArrowLeft':\n                case 'KeyA':\n                    if (direction.x !== 1) {\n                        nextDirection = { x: -1, y: 0 };\n                    }\n                    break;\n                case 'ArrowRight':\n                case 'KeyD':\n                    if (direction.x !== -1) {\n                        nextDirection = { x: 1, y: 0 };\n                    }\n                    break;\n                case 'KeyP':\n                    if (gameState === 'playing') {\n                        gameState = 'paused';\n                        pauseScreen.classList.remove('hidden');\n                    } else if (gameState === 'paused') {\n                        gameState = 'playing';\n                        pauseScreen.classList.add('hidden');\n                    }\n                    break;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 游戏循环\n        function gameLoop(currentTime) {\n            deltaTime = currentTime - lastTime;\n            lastTime = currentTime;\n            \n            update(deltaTime);\n            render();\n            \n            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 事件监听\n        document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {\n            handleInput(e.code, true);\n        });\n        \n        document.getElementById('startButton').addEventListener('click', () => {\n            resetGame();\n            gameState = 'playing';\n            menuScreen.classList.add('hidden');\n        });\n        \n        document.getElementById('resumeButton').addEventListener('click', () => {\n            gameState = 'playing';\n            pauseScreen.classList.add('hidden');\n        });\n        \n        document.getElementById('restartButton').addEventListener('click', () => {\n            resetGame();\n            gameState = 'playing';\n            gameOverScreen.classList.add('hidden');\n        });\n        \n        // 初始化游戏\n        function init() {\n            updateUI();\n            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);\n        }\n        \n        // 启动游戏\n        init();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
